full_summary:
=====================================

### Global Tender Announcement

#### Firing Mechanism for Machine Gun

The Department of National Defence invites bids for the procurement of Firing Mechanism components for Machine Gun systems. The delivery locations for this procurement are:

* Canadian Forces Base (CFB) Halifax, Nova Scotia
* CFB Esquimalt, British Columbia

**Summary of Requirements**

* Items to be procured: Lock, Breech, Machine Gun (CB-6462-34545682)
* Quantity: 100 pieces (50 for each location)
* Specification: GSIN: N1005, NSN: 01-0419393, Part No.: 11691480, NCAGE: 19204, UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF THE ARMY

**Important Requirements and Terms**

* Bidders proposing equivalent or substitute products must provide the brand name and model, and/or Part Number, and the NCAGE they are offering.
* All bids must be submitted in Canadian dollars. Bids submitted in foreign currency will not be considered.
* The Crown retains the right to negotiate with suppliers on any procurement.
* Documents may be submitted in either official language of Canada.

**Trade Agreements and Preferences**

* Preference will be given to Canadian goods and/or services.
* This tender is subject to the provisions of the Agreement on Internal Trade (AIT) and the North American Free Trade Agreement (NAFTA).

**Procurement Information**

* Solicitation Number: W8482-241722/A
* Tender Closing Date: 2023-07-17T14:00:00
* Registration Information: Please register on the Buy and Sell website (canadabuys.canada.ca) to receive further information and to submit your bid.

**Contact Information**

* Name: Christopher Cauchi
* Email: christopher.cauchi@forces.gc.ca
* Phone: (555) 555-5555
* Address: 101 Colonel By Drive, Ottawa, ON, Canada, K1A 0K2

**Additional Resources**

* Tender Description: *[Lock, Breech, Machine Gun - CB-6462-34545682](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/6462/w8482-241722---rfp---en.pdf)*
